div.p: I'm a software engineer that transitioned from a customer service background because I got tired of being forced to use bad software to do my job - I knew by leveraging my experience and knowledge I could make a better product myself!
So, I built Magical Merchant - a POS system anyone can use on mobile and PC without any extra hardware - You can check it out along with my other projects below.
Bootstrap, Sass, Express.js, + MongoDB - A web-based point of sale system that your small business can run anywhere and take card payments without needing a pin pad.
EJS + Node.js - A Restful API serving Guilty Gear Strive data, plus scripting to automate web scraping the data and an app utilizing the API.
HTML5, CSS3, + Jekyll - My portfolio and blog site showcasing what I'm building, stuff I'm learning, and how to contact me.
HTML5, CSS3, + JavaScript - A local antique and art store that has been in business for over 30 years commissioned me to build their first website.
